<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta http-equiv="x-ua-compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>Reset Password Email</title>
</head>

<body>
    <div style=" 
        padding: 26px;
        text-align: center;
        width: 375px;
        border-radius: 6px;
        box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px 2px rgb(156, 156, 156);">
        <h1 style="color: #00b8d4;">TechForum</h1>
        <hr>
        <h2>Password Reset</h2>
        <h4>Hello {{name}} </h4>
        <p>We have recived a request to reset the password for the emailId: {{emailId}}.</p>
        <p>You can reset your password by clicking the link below:</p>
        <a href="{{link}}">
            <button style="
            background-color: #00b8d4;
            color: white;
            width: 250px;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 16px;">Reset your password</button></a>
        <p>If you didn't request for reset password, please let us know immediately by replying to this email</p>
        <p>-TechForum team</p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>